metadata.name: A Crackling Lighthouse Of Synthetic Waves
metadata.description:
Music, my true lighthouse, my guide in the turbulent and chaotic sea of life. In my retro-futuristic environment, between the vintage crackling noise of a vinyl record player and the cyberpunk-inspired synthetic sound waves, I always feel hypnotized and amazed by it. I feel good, and I dream.

I hope you can feel the same by watching and listening to this piece of art/music.
